snippet.title: Johnny Depp vs Amber Heard Trial Live Coverage Day 1
snippet.description:
The trial we have all been waiting for has arrived. It may well be that this first day ends up being a no show for the court cam, as there will be Jury selection happening, however, I will still be streaming and chatting about the case too. Let the show begin

My co host throughout will be the wonderful ClaireS who has her own channel too and is going to be a fantastic addition to this stream. Her channel is https://www.youtube.com/c/ClaireView307

Would you like to support that efforts of me and my channel and see it grow? 
Paypal? https://www.paypal.com/paypalme/RantyFE

Support the channel on Patreon? https://www.patreon.com/flerfspective

If anyone wants to adopt a Flerf, or any of the other levels https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw1Y...

Follow me on Twitter https://twitter.com/AuditTheAbsurd
